Darla Sinnard, Regional Manager, Jennings Realty
With 30 years of experience in the hospitality industry, Darla provides a unique understanding of customer service, resort management and industry knowledge to our guests. She currently manages operations for Jennings Realty’s highly rated Bay Bayou RV Resort in Tampa FL, and is instrumental in the planning, development and management of our new Resort, Sunkissed Village RV Resort in Summerfield, FL. Darla is currently serving her first term as Secretary on the Board of Directors for the FL/AL Association of RV Parks and Campgrounds and is actively involved in all aspects of the RV industry. Rymer Companies
Rymer Companies is a diversified, privately held real-estate investment company. More than 35 years of broad-based experience in development, owning and managing of investment real estate.
President and CEO Ed Rymer attributes much of his success to having a keen eye for an opportunity and surrounding himself with a group of talented, results-oriented individuals.
Jennings Realty, Inc.
Jennings Realty is a fourth generation, family owned real estate investment company that owns and operates Recreational Vehicle and Manufactured Home communities in Illinois and Florida. Jennings Realty has been involved in the management and ownership of Recreational Vehicle resorts for over two decades and prides itself on retaining experienced, professional staff and a desire to exceed our guest’s expectations by providing excellent customer service and the ultimate resort experience at our properties. Our most recent endeavor is the development of Sunkissed Village RV Resort, a 267-site luxury RV Resort and park model community in Summerfield, FL, located near The Villages, rated one of the best retirement areas in the country.
